latestPosts.caption:
My daily glow comes from little acts of self care. From prioritising movement in the form of pilates and yoga, to using vitamin-enriched skincare, it’s all about the small things that make a big difference - inside and out 🤍

@bobbibrownindia #MyDailyGlow#VitaminEnriched #BobbiBrownIndia

My PM skincare routine is incomplete without the La Mer Eye Concentrate 
I find myself reaching for the little green jar to reduce the look of dark circles and fine lines that come with age. It is formulated with Concentrated Miracle Broth™️ that delivers healing hydration to the eye area. 
My favourite beauty hack is to pop the applicator in the fridge for a few minutes to support micro circulation. Try it for bright and revitalised look ✨

Shop now at @tirabeauty 

#LaMerIndia #LaMer
